original_title: เหนือธรรมชาติ
overview: Science fiction about a future Thailand. Futuristic, experimental, homo-erotic and with elements of a political essay. With a richness of themes and impressions that wouldn’t get past the censor in Thailand. The maker doesn’t mince his words and isn’t afraid to look reality in the eye.
tagline: He who controls the past controls the future.
title: Supernatural
